And he just sat there right next to me and as Clover and I began walking back to the chairs, getting as many of these seashells as we can, at which point I immediately looked up and he was right there behind our chairs looking at us, looking for his opportunity to get him again with a smug look on his face.

00:41:31.458 --> 00:41:36.243
